EN: This company lowered wages to reduce operating costs.

ZH: 他的坚持压低了他的威信。
EN: His persistence lowered his reputation.

ZH: 压低音量会减少噪音的干扰。
EN: Lowering the volume will reduce the interference of noise.

ZH: 他压低了自己的期望以应对失败。
EN: He lowered his expectations to cope with failure.

ZH: 压低生活水平会影响人们的幸福感。
EN: Lowering the standard of living affects people's sense of happiness.

ZH: 他压低了桌子的高度以适应他的身高。
EN: He lowered the height of the table to suit his height.
